Flashcard:
Front: Creating a Reply with Custom Headers
Back: Use `warp_replies::with_header` to set custom headers in a Reply. Example:
```rust
use warp::reply::{self, with_header};

let response = reply::with_header(
    reply::status(200),
    "Content-Type".to_string(),
    "text/plain".to_string()
);
```

